sequenceDiagram
    participant LS as Language Server<br/>（rust-analyzer/pyright）
    participant LC as LSPClient.ts<br/>stdio + JSON-RPC
    participant DR as LSPDiagnosticRegistry
    participant PF as passiveFeedback.ts
    participant CTX as Agent 对话上下文

    LS->>LC: publishDiagnostics 通知（JSON-RPC）
    LC->>PF: 转发诊断数据
    PF->>DR: registerPendingLSPDiagnostic()<br/>attachmentSent = false
    Note over DR: 缓存等待注入时机
    CTX->>DR: 新一轮对话开始
    DR->>CTX: 注入诊断附件<br/>attachmentSent → true
